Mobile Football Agent 

Have you ever dreamed of becoming a famous football agent? Here is the opportunity. 
Become one of the most important people in the football world.
Enjoy the management agency you set up with many famous players. 
Deal with surprise dilemmas and events and keep your players happy in this adventure.
Help the young stars you discover climb the career ladder. 
Don't forget to get your own commission by making deals with the clubs to get them the best players. 
You can also build relationships with the best clubs in the world. 
Grow your agency with the money you earn, buy new items from the store and gain reputation in the football world. 
Make the right decisions for their careers by sending your players who have not had the chance to form to the right clubs. 
Experience the excitement of discovering new players by opening packages. 
Achieve success with the new players you discover and progress towards becoming the number one manager of the football world. 
Step into this huge world without waiting and experience a unique career of football agent.

